===票房===
《国际机场》于1970年3月5日发行上映，售出电影票6611万1300张，票房收入高达1亿零48万9151美元，考虑[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]因素则相当于2013年的5亿3219万5800美元，在历史上所有电影中名列第43位<ref name="Box Office Mojo">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=airport.htm |title=Box Office Mojo: Airport |accessdate=2013-03-31 |archive-date=2014-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140405015227/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=airport.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===评论===
《[[综艺|综艺]]》杂志介绍这部电影为“根据阿瑟·米勒同名小说改编，罗斯·亨特担任制作人，演员表中的明星名单就像是机场跑道那么长，乔治·希顿改编剧本并亲自执导的一部表面光鲜但却华而不实的电影。”“《国际机场》就像是用一大堆明星和高达一千万美元的成本，堆砌成昔日所有能代表成功电影的名字们共同的墓志铭”。并且影片情节上也“没有任何悬念，因为观众都知道接下来会发生些什么<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117796712.html?categoryid=31&cs=1&p=0 |title=''Variety,'' Review of ''Airport'', Thursday, January 1, 1970 |accessdate=2013-03-31 |archive-date=2020-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319003421/https://www.variety.com/review/VE1117796712.html?categoryid=31&cs=1&p=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

现代的电影评论家则大多给予影片严厉的批准<ref name="Roger Ebert">{{cite news |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19700101/REVIEWS/1010301/1023 |title=Ebert's review of 'Airport' |work=《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》 |accessdate=2020-10-04 |archive-date=2013-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130309234742/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19700101%2FREVIEWS%2F1010301%2F1023 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Ozus' World Movie Reviews">{{cite web |url=http://www.sover.net/~ozus/airport.htm |title=Airport review |access-date=2013-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080616091651/http://www.sover.net/~ozus/airport.htm |archive-date=2008-06-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而对该片最为宽厚的评价则主要称赞了影片对[[灾难片|灾难片]]类型电影所产生的影响等<ref name="New York Times">{{cite news |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9E0DEFDB1638EE34BC4E53DFB566838B669EDE |title=The Screen: Multi-Plot, Multi-Star 'Airport' Opens: Lancaster and Martin in Principal Roles Adaptation of Hailey's Novel at Music Hall |work=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》 |first=Vincent |last=Canby |date=1970-03-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102005806/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9E0DEFDB1638EE34BC4E53DFB566838B669EDE |archivedate=2013-11-02 |accessdate=2013-03-31 }}</ref><ref name="filmcritic">{{cite web |url=http://www.filmcritic.com/misc/emporium.nsf/reviews/Airport |title=filmcritic: Airport |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100202220109/http://www.filmcritic.com/misc/emporium.nsf/reviews/Airport |archivedate=2010-02-02 |accessdate=2013-03-31 }}</ref>。

